{"tid":2016038,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"網民大發現！ OnePlus 8 Pro 相機濾鏡竟可透視膠殼內部元件","createTime":"2020-05-14T06:05:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T17:29:20.000Z","uid":1121,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"a459331798d9a49a36ae7d1103c388f64232d159","tid":2016038,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T06:05:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://pc3mag.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/oneplus-8-pro-x-ray-mode-camera_01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpc3mag.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2Foneplus-8-pro-x-ray-mode-camera_01.jpg&h=dcfecbaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n紅外線透視大家聽得多，但最近有不少網民在 OnePlus 8 Pro 發現一個可以透視一個膠殼裝置內部元件的方法。<br />\n<br />\n爆料達人 Ben Geskin 在 Twitter 分享影片，說他在 OnePlus 8 Pro 相機開 Photochrom 濾鏡之後，竟發現會對塑膠表面有紅外線透視效果，就像照 X 光一樣透視膠殼內部的元件，他使用 Apple TV 電視盒和 Oculus Quest 控制器進行示範，原本要拆解才會看到的內部金屬元件完全顯現出來。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://pc3mag.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/oneplus-8-pro-x-ray-mode-camera_02.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpc3mag.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2Foneplus-8-pro-x-ray-mode-camera_02.jpeg&h=6a74a440&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nOnePlus 8 Pro Photochrom 濾鏡是否能透視衣服？有外媒曾經試過，雖則可以透視到衣服內裡的字條，但你不能看到其他東西，大家別想邪。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://pc3mag.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/oneplus-8-pro-x-ray-mode-camera_03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpc3mag.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2Foneplus-8-pro-x-ray-mode-camera_03.jpg&h=9edbccd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n會發生這種情況，有相機專家指一般相機會有紅外濾鏡阻擋可見光譜之外的光線，防止紅外線干擾及影響最終圖像質素，但某些相機可能會允許少部分紅外線滲入，就像 OnePlus 8 Pro 般，才會出現透視膠殼這個效果。"},{"pid":"c516f6880f35347cd1cf0db7b8043f1ab3a79715","tid":2016038,"uid":36791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T06:09:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a42393e3219ad52d28eefbb47802066475ccb73","tid":2016038,"uid":1